      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DIM SIM RIXI (5) was game in defeat off the inside draw last start, finishing second and beaten half a length (19.75) behind Skeeter Mikado at Healesville. Sure to be about the mark. DOOKIE GIBLET (6) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish third (22.81) at Ballarat in a Grade 5 over 390m. Expected to feature again. WESTERN FEEL (1) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when sixth at Warragul over 400m behind Jumping Oreo (23.49) in a Grade 5. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Should be about the mark. WE ARE SOUTH (2) can return to form after missing the top-three at this circuit last time out.",
